        <TD bgcolor='black' valign='top'><font color='white' face='Verdana' size='2'> Dark Elves and Iksar are feared and respected in their home towns and are not KoS (both races only have evils).  Heretic Erudites have thier own town, Paineel, though you will run into problems in erudin.  Humans and gnomes operate from the sewers and abandoned mines of their cities and as they do evil (quests, kill good faction) they become dubious and KoS in the mainstream parts of thier towns.</P><P>Dark Elves are the evilest race, followed closely by the Iksar.  Both seek world domination though thier respective philosophies (hate and fear).  I think the dark reflection (evil gnomes) seeks to eventually take over A'kanon and promote decay.  Humans promote either hate or diseases.</P><P>Suetekh<BR>Necromancer of 34 Reanimations</font></td>
